{"about_the_game":"In the past, the insatiable greed of jinns and mythical creatures led to the splitting of the crystal into six parts, dispersing them to all corners of the world.<br><br>Manipulation, provocation, and incitement are tactics consistently employed by jinns to reclaim the entirety of the crystal's power.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/Roaming_Heroes.gif?t=1727497790\" /><br>In the medieval era, a child chosen by the gods possesses a unique talent. Utilize these abilities to rescue the crystal from malevolence and avert the world's impending destruction.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/Key_Feature.jpg?t=1727497790\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/Main_Heroes_Remake.gif?t=1727497790\" /><br>Each character possesses varying strengths, exhibiting unique personalities and fighting styles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/Diverse_Heroes_Strengths.jpg?t=1727497790\" /><br>Each region harbors formidable heroes, each with distinct abilities and summoning capabilities.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/Various_Types_of_Khodam.jpg?t=1727497790\" /><br>A supernatural protective figure is possessed by heroes in various regions, each having different powers and origins according to their owners.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765090/extras/Turn-Base_Battles.gif?t=1727497790\" /><br>Experience the excitement of turn-based combat, leveraging the unique skills of each hero. Strategize by combining their abilities for optimal effectiveness.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:/